        <body>
                <div1>
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a01"/>大魏正光五年歲次甲辰七月己酉朔廿
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a02"/>五日癸酉。故蘭倉令孫府君浮圖之銘記。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a03"/>君姓孫。名遼。<note n="0060001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30070;＝定【中研院】</note><app n="0060001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">定</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30070;</rdg></app>州人也。綿緒太原。分流樂 
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a04"/>安。爵土有因。遂居鉅鹿<note n="0060002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30485;＝焉【中研院】</note><app n="0060002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">焉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30485;</rdg></app>。君稟業沖明。惠
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a05"/>性天<note n="0060003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02194;＝聰【中研院】</note><app n="0060003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">聰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02194;</rdg></app>。少懷淨行。長而彌潔。悟三有之&CB07099;
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a06"/>常。體四趣之沈溺。洞達苦空。超鑒十相。是
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a07"/>以童丱之年。信心三寶。厥齡十八。禁酒斷
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a08"/><note n="0060004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18861;＝肉【中研院】</note><app n="0060004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">肉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18861;</rdg></app>。脩齋持戒。心無染縛。善能開化。方便導
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a09"/>物。聞其善者。欣若己身。見其<note n="0060005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08891;＝惡【中研院】</note><app n="0060005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">惡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08891;</rdg></app>者。引出火
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a10"/>宅。又不以支節之痛。亦其&CB07099;我之念。遂燒
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a11"/>兩指。盡身供養。至<note n="0060006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30487;＝於【中研院】</note><app n="0060006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30487;</rdg></app>經行業道之處。必捨
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a12"/>離親愛。敦崇在內。託心禪<note n="0060007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30070;＝定【中研院】</note><app n="0060007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">定</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30070;</rdg></app>。永樂道場。至
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a13"/>延昌年中。屬　皇上宣帝。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">褒</unclear>&CB01826;<note n="0060008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30493;＝舊【中研院】</note><app n="0060008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30493;</rdg></app>臣。即拜
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a14"/>前縣。辭不獲免。俯仰從任。善<note n="0060009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30487;＝於【中研院】</note><app n="0060009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30487;</rdg></app>治方。敷揚
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a15"/>恩澤。化均魯恭。德侔西門。名振關左。限過
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a16"/>將代。百姓愛仰。率土戀慕。若失慈父。還京
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a17"/>數年。仍懃道業。將登顯位。以　彰庸績。春
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a18"/>秋六十七。前件年日。寢疾三朝。<note n="0060010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18847;＝卒【中研院】</note><app n="0060010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">卒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18847;</rdg></app><note n="0060011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30487;＝於【中研院】</note><app n="0060011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30487;</rdg></app>京師。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a19"/><note n="0060012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30488;＝權【中研院】</note><app n="0060012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30488;</rdg></app>殯此處。有子顯就。靈鳳。子沖等。追述亡
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a20"/>考。精誠之功。敬造浮圖一<note n="0060013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00100;＝區【中研院】</note><app n="0060013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00100;</rdg></app>。置<note n="0060014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30487;＝於【中研院】</note><app n="0060014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30487;</rdg></app>　墓所。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a21"/>願令事与須彌等壽。理与日月齊明。永流
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a22"/>懿&CB00528;。式傳不朽。迺作銘曰。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a23"/>二儀無像。四天傳則。靈<note n="0060015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB09400;＝剎【中研院】</note><app n="0060015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">剎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB09400;</rdg></app>開神。梵堂<note n="0060016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30318;＝&CB30397;【中研院】</note><app n="0060016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">&CB30397;</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30318;</rdg></app><note n="0060017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30489;＝或【中研院】</note><app n="0060017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">或</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30489;</rdg></app>。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a24"/>伊我君公。秉心淵默。深&CB00418;正真。妙達通塞。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a25"/>淹迴聖&CB00528;。寢息神光。裁辯<note n="0060018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30488;＝權【中研院】</note><app n="0060018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30488;</rdg></app>實。離<note n="0060019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30490;＝柝【中研院】</note><app n="0060019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">柝</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30490;</rdg></app><note n="0060020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30493;＝舊【中研院】</note><app n="0060020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30493;</rdg></app><note n="0060021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30494;＝章【中研院】</note><app n="0060021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">章</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30494;</rdg></app>。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a26"/>十塵外遣。五陰內忘。蒸斯沈溺。作彼舟<note n="0060022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11970;＝航【中研院】</note><app n="0060022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">航</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11970;</rdg></app>。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a27"/>出宿一<note n="0060023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02391;＝廛【中研院】</note><app n="0060023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">廛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02391;</rdg></app>。遄臨百里。秋蝗遠飛。春翬近止。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a28"/>清淨未儔。&CB01826;率誰擬。方覲彌陀。遽淪濛汜。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a29"/>咨余小子。末命將淪。構茲寶塔。綴此遺塵。
                         <lb ed="I" n="0060a30"/>崇功去劫。樹善來因。舟壑雖改。永播天人。
                </div1>
